CFN2AC7HPR2RI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210502%2FZRNNKDHTF5F75CFN2AC7HPR2RI%2F&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNur6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=6f16b304\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210502%2FZRNNKDHTF5F75CFN2AC7HPR2RI%2F&h=de8a0a67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210502/ZRNNKDHTF5F75CFN2AC7HPR2RI/</a><br />\n<br />\n姜濤壓力爆煲暈倒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pB86jRmRQBjJWSt1SINf9Ox0xMc=/624x603/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QQPE75YG55HT5HZ4WTDVFYY4KM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpB86jRmRQBjJWSt1SINf9Ox0xMc%3D%2F624x603%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQQPE75YG55HT5HZ4WTDVFYY4KM.jpg&h=8e49d44c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■姜濤昨日凌晨開直播，自言近日壓力大，情緒亦很差。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n人氣王姜濤前日22歲生日，「姜糖」花近百萬在銅鑼灣、中環及尖沙嘴等地大賣廣告祝壽，還有電車及巴士廣告，把他現居的銅鑼灣打造成「姜濤灣」。為答謝「姜糖」支持，姜B昨日凌晨1時在Ig開直播跟姜糖傾偈，高峯時有逾萬人收看，但他全程表現身心俱疲，除再三多謝姜糖的支持及送上的生日祝福外，他亦自爆近月來情緒極差：「呢段時間發生好多嘢，確實未消化得晒，攞到獎當然係好事，但同時壓力亦大咗好多，尤其呢排情緒好差，直到兩日前都成日發脾氣，希望之前因我發脾氣而影響到嘅人，講聲唔好意思。」其間姜B重提梅窩事件，再向fans道歉，另外談到好友猝死：「件事被傳媒寫咗出嚟，影響到佢嘅家人，唔好意思。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LT7oZQnoz__fiPbAT2rMrrl2ZAc=/624x936/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6O5HOFGCSFF6NEZJRW5UDLWQZI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLT7oZQnoz__fiPbAT2rMrrl2ZAc%3D%2F624x936%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6O5HOFGCSFF6NEZJRW5UDLWQZI.jpg&h=baa42e26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■姜濤近日為MIRROR今個月的九展騷進行密集式綵排。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n向Candy致歉<br />\n<br />\n姜濤在直播時自爆日前排舞時暈倒：「我事後先知道，可能真係太眼瞓、太攰，有啲暈，加上全日冇乜食嘢。好白癡呀&hellip;&hellip;呢件事，咁我有食返嘢嘅，所以大家唔使擔心。」他透露演唱會後會放長假處理私事，不少姜糖叮囑他好好休息。尾聲時，姜濤亦有提到與「YOLO女」黃曦誼（Candy）傳緋聞：「真係一個誤會，新聞出街後睇到留言係咁鬧佢，想同佢講唔好意思。」昨日更有報道指，姜濤工作不絕，近半年內保守估計已吸金逾200萬，認真厲害。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T03:42:38.000Z","msg":"吸金200萬禁小？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該唔止"},{"pid":"7da3e650cd56aad2963f685026e974ce2af9ff91","tid":2512643,"uid":356906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T03:43:17.000Z","msg":"見到留言窒佢嗰啲來來去去都個幾個名大家知咩事啦<br />\n<br />\n人哋又冇抱怨只不過係講件事出嚟，講出嚟都唔得呀？"},{"pid":"c6b50a0793c41fbe68ebe8f6c423500d1ce08c7c","tid":2512643,"uid":19196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T03:43:32.000Z","msg":"姜b<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c9cd69496a2d9f1879845edb214adfcae5509d","tid":2512643,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"06db4ff8d25ab9069a76115a5f2c9db404c75f26","tid":2512643,"uid":101548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"425e76b4b124c7fd41254ea191c9a05f14194f05","tid":2512643,"uid":5378,"like":44,"dislike":3,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T03:03:33.000Z","msg":"相信best fd 係自己眼前過身先係最頂唔順既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T03:33:53.000Z","msg":"同意，佢出道前得2個朋友，一個係打波時係你面前過身喎。正常人都難克服啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T03:43:51.000Z","msg":"感情用事"},{"pid":"1251f7d46df195053fb761a07a6583d0072a71df","tid":2512643,"uid":369685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ceb5b94e4aa52e24e48c7872c83e993c3b67b4b9","tid":2512643,"uid":140365,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"95a1852f9c9270bfadf669dcf6076fdb2ef02a80","tid":2512643,"uid":172190,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"c091b4b9d9f91308ec4250c842966ef086743717","tid":2512643,"uid":294,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:20:45.000Z","msg":"賺錢咁易咩"